HEADWORD: Superroyal
<hw>Su`per*roy"al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Larger than
royal; -- said of a particular size of printing and writing paper. See
the Note under <er>Paper</er>, <pos>n.</pos></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

